title: Daily: Naming & shaming Iran's hackers? Palo Alto spots "Digital Quartermaster." Team Apple bigger than Team DoJ.
description: Daily: Naming & shaming Iran's hackers? Palo Alto spots "Digital Quartermaster." Team Apple bigger than Team DoJ. Plus, Jonathan Katz from the Maryland Cyber Security Center responds to Richard Clarke's NPR interview. Are claims of NSA's capabilities grounded in reality?
